{"tid":2290432,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"「咁咩案件都可以搵國安法嘅官審㗎啦」#快必案","createTime":"2020-11-18T04:02:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-18T04:02:11.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"826e8c7b1a824b93a3279bf8c326007cd04a2c97","tid":2290432,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T04:02:11.000Z","msg":"「咁咩案件都可以搵國安法嘅官審㗎啦」#快必案<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201118/2TWS6UOXYJCTPBJWKGCSPYVA2Q/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201118%2F2TWS6UOXYJCTPBJWKGCSPYVA2Q%2F&d=KoeRi8LHiva86SpHjnbz1fY%2F4yEwT0EAZMYNsJUacQ0%3D&h=43dfd970\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201118%2F2TWS6UOXYJCTPBJWKGCSPYVA2Q%2F&h=e561c73d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201118/2TWS6UOXYJCTPBJWKGCSPYVA2Q/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n快必無涉國安罪 控方申國安官審 <br />\n慢必轟律政司︰無所不用其極<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/WVBnce5w41BXX7NQ4wFQOpV8jdI=/720x461/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/C56M26SEPZAC7I5I4MGHP45C7U.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FWVBnce5w41BXX7NQ4wFQOpV8jdI%3D%2F720x461%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FC56M26SEPZAC7I5I4MGHP45C7U.jpg&h=ac846ec0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■譚得志因擺街站被控串謀發表煽惑文字等14罪。<br />\n<br />\n【法庭直擊】<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】人民力量副主席「快必」譚得志因擺街站被控串謀發表煽惑文字等14罪，雖然控方並非以國安法起訴，但繼上次「加建」指控他意圖改變香港法律地位，昨進一步要求本案由國安法指定法官審理。辯方反對，指被告涉嫌干犯的罪行不涉危害國家安全。有律師批評，律政司並非以國安法起訴，根本沒法理依據要求由指定法官審案，若法庭接納，則暴動甚至破壞交通設施也可指控危害國家安全，交由國安法的官審理。<br />\n<br />\n被告譚得志（48歲）被控14項控罪，當中包括發表煽惑文字罪，其餘為舉行或召集未經批准公眾集會、在公眾地方內擾亂秩序的行為等罪，案件昨在區院首度提訊。控方引用港區國安法第44條申請由指定法官處理本案，又指若案件交由非指定法官處理，可能引起司法覆核。代表譚的資深大律師戴啟思反對，指被告所犯的罪不涉危害國家安全；另一位辯方大狀譚俊傑亦認為控方想法過慮。根據國安法第44條，行政長官應當從各級法院指定若干名法官，負責處理危害國家安全犯罪案件。法官高勁修將案件押後至下月2日，以聆聽雙方進一步陳詞。自今年9月提堂後一直還柙的譚，昨申請保釋再被拒。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/zC7Uc22aMomz-9mA7YPHQLPj5zw=/1332x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/NMCSIRELWNFL3MIJ6LUCQUXZH4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FzC7Uc22aMomz-9mA7YPHQLPj5zw%3D%2F1332x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FNMCSIRELWNFL3MIJ6LUCQUXZH4.jpg&h=01c4ba1d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■慢必陳志全散庭後對控方做法大表不滿，直言政府對抗爭者無所不用其極 。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/5OJwbqvMDizNUNaIluypN2kRIMs=/1329x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/7M3NQQJ3QNBMPJZO4WFN6SANIY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F5OJwbqvMDizNUNaIluypN2kRIMs%3D%2F1329x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F7M3NQQJ3QNBMPJZO4WFN6SANIY.jpg&h=ce3b5342&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■快必昨申請保釋再被拒，乘囚車離開法院時，支持者紛紛叫「想我收聲，我更大聲」等口號。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n律師指沒法理依據<br />\n<br />\n。。。。。。。。。。。慢必陳志全昨散庭後批評，譚被控的罪行並沒涉及國安法，「只要控方話你嘅行為有機會危害國家安全，就算用唔到國安法告你，都可以叫國安處查你」，第二步將審訊升至較高級法院處理，第三步便是申請用指定法官處理，陳直言政府對抗爭者無所不用其極。<br />\n<br />\n控方本月初就本案所有發。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n律師文浩正表示，是以《刑事訴訟條例》以及《公安條例》起訴譚，理應沒法理依據要求國安法指定法官審理此案，「個申請真係好奇怪」。律政司或會以案件性質違反危害國家安全為由提出申請，若按此說法，其他案件如暴動罪、破壞交通設施等根據國安法條文均會危害國家安全，<span class=\"orange\">「咁咩案件都可以搵國安法嘅官審㗎啦」</span>。<br />\n<br />\n案件編號：DCCC 927-930/20<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/oRl3BxCvMjq25XhdGPkCZ9U6ED0=/1329x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/EN7GACS3GNEDDMYPXDJMIVUYQ4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FoRl3BxCvMjq25XhdGPkCZ9U6ED0%3D%2F1329x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FEN7GACS3GNEDDMYPXDJMIVUYQ4.jpg&h=ea191ce3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n律政司長鄭若驊"}]}